        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/mujam-al-ahadith-al-mutabara:3:13:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/3/13/3",
        "text": [
          ": سألت أبا عبد الله عليه السلام عن أحاديث جابر فقال: ما رأيته عند أبي قط إلا مرة واحدة و ما دخل علي قط"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.ammaar-muslim": [
            "3. [3/137] Rijal al-Kashshi: Hamduwayh and Ibrahim the two sons of Nusayr from Muhammad b. Isa from Ali b. al-Hakam from Ibn Bukayr from Zurara who said: I asked Aba Abdillah عليه السلام about the narrations of Jabir, he said: I never saw him with my father – ever – except for one time, and he never entered upon me [to take Hadith] ever."
          ]
        }
